<html>
    <head>
        <title>{{ project.getName }}: {{ step.getDescription }}</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Great. Glad you feel confident you can complete this step.</h1>
        <p>Let me know when you've finished it.</p>

        <form action="/coach/active_project/{{ project.getId }}/complete" method="post">
            <input type="hidden" name="step_id" value="{{ step.getId }}">
            <input type="checkbox" name="completed" value="true" onchange="this.form.submit();"
                 {% if step.getCompleted == true %} checked{% endif %}>
             I finished this task!!!!!!
        </form>

        (( check box here in form that posts to this same address))
        <p><a href="/coach/active_project/{{ project.getId }}/next_step">I'm ready for the next step.</a></p>
        <p><a href="/coach/active_project/{{ project.getId }}/enough">That's enough for right now.</a></p>
    </body>
</html>
